        <paragraph align="center">○<index num="0262537_0" ref="M_0036364" sort="K" type="이름">魯山君</index>諱<index num="0262538_0" ref="M_0036364" sort="K" type="이름">弘暐</index>, <index num="0262539_0" ref="M_0046153" sort="K" type="이름">文宗恭順王</index>一子, 母<index num="0262540_0" ref="M_0006821" sort="K" type="이름">權氏</index>。 <index num="0262541_0" type="연호">正統</index>六年辛酉七月丁巳生, 戊辰四月戊午<index num="0262542_0" ref="M_0032471" sort="K" type="이름">世宗</index>封王世孫, <index num="0262543_0" type="연호">景泰</index>元年庚午八月, <index num="0262544_0" ref="M_0046153" sort="K" type="이름">文宗</index>遣領議政<index num="0262545_0" ref="M_0006730" sort="K" type="이름">皇甫仁</index>, 請爲國儲, 辛未正月, 皇帝勑封爲王世子。 三年壬申五月丙午, <index num="0262546_0" ref="M_0046153" sort="K" type="이름">文宗</index>薨于<index num="0262547_0" sort="K" type="지명">景福宮</index>
          <index num="0262548_0" sort="K" type="지명">千秋殿</index>。 議政府奉<index num="0262549_0" ref="M_0036364" sort="K" type="이름">魯山君</index>, 入處<index num="0262550_0" sort="K" type="지명">含元殿</index>。</paragraph>
